{
  "stem": "25178.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For some reason, they, they knew that I was not priest material.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So after about two years, they decided, you know, that it was no use for me to go on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So when I did my finals, after the finals were over, he came to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he sent me away to the ocean for a couple of months to a family who was doing this as a charity to take care of displaced persons.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was there for about two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then he called me home again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he said, I had to go and get a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I couldn't go back to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it's about time that I should earn some money to support-- help support the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he got me a job in Westmalle in a local bakery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And at night, I was learning how to bake bread, and during the day I was delivering the bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I did that for about one year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that one year, I got a job for a man who had a camera store in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he asked me one time when I met him, he said, are you interested in photography?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I don't even know what photography is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, well, I'm looking for somebody I can teach how to print.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Would you be interested?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, I have to talk to, to this man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to call him [FLEMISH] that was Flemish for father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, you have to ask [FLEMISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when he heard that the guy was paying me a nice salary, of course, I got the job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was traveling to Antwerp every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this man taught me how to print.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
